Package edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActionInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Action, AttackAction, BreedAction, DieAction, DoNothingAction, DropItemAction, EatAction, FeedAction, KickAction, LayEggAction, MoveActorAction, PickUpItemAction, Player.SleepAction, PurchaseAction, SearchFruitAction, SpitBehaviour, WindowSmashAction
    public interface ActionInterface
    This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.
